title: The She Beast English Version With Italian Subtitles

sources.title: The She Beast English Version With Italian Subtitles
sources.description: A young woman is driving alongside a lake. She has an accident and the car plunges into the water. Her body is then possessed by the spirit of an 18th-century witch who was killed by local villagers, and is bent on avenging herself on them. In English with Italian subtitles.
